Class Water

  • java.lang.Object
    • physicalLayer.CellObject
      • physicalLayer.Water

  • public class Water
extends CellObject
    A class to model a dangerous Water object, which has a depth. Objects can be placed in it to reduce depth.
    Version:
    v1.2
    Author:
    Chloe M. Barnes
